(4, 'mutual-fund', 'Mutual Funds', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"product_text\">\r\n<p>Mutual funds have emerged as an attractive investment option for investors, as indicated by the recent sharp growth in industry assets. Professional fund management, diversification, liquidity, and reasonable cost build a strong case for mutual funds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One&rsquo;s goal, investment horizon, and risk profile determines the choice of your schemes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One should remember that the investment universe of schemes has a big impact on the risk element in it. That is why you need to choose an advisor that will help pick schemes as per your risk appetite.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From the plethora schemes offered by over 20plus AMCs, we at Advisor Zaroori Hai help you to select the right mutual fund that meets your needs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
(5, 'pms', 'Portfolio Managment Services', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"product_text\">\r\n<p>PMS helps to increase or subsequently grow the wealth of the investor with their knowledge and skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is often found that HNIs looking for high value returns struggle when it comes to selecting the right mix of investments and make smart investment decisions as per their risk appetite and financial objective. Thereby they require a professional financial advisor who can invest money on their behalf .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advisor Zaroori Hai understands that picking the right PMS from among the many could be puzzling but we assure you that with the help of our pool of experienced advisors, you&rsquo;ll be glad that you took the time to find the ideal one.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
(6, 'aif', 'Alternate Investment Fund', '<div class=\"product_text\"><p> AIFs are a class of pooled-in vehicles for investing in real estate, private equity and hedge funds.</p><p> Traditionally, the only way to create financial assets in India was to put your money in conventional investment categories such as stocks, bonds, and real estate. With the increasing tribe of high net-worth individuals in the country, there is a steady rise in the demand for non-conventional investment avenues such as Alternative Investment Funds (AIFs).</p><p> Alternative investment funds are complex and often higher risk than traditional investments that is why a professional financial advisor is required to invest money appropriately inorder for it to grow over time.</p><p>That\'s why at Advisor Zaroori Hai, we’ve built a network of the best advise providers to assist you in growing your wealth .</p></div>'),
(7, 'equity', 'Equity', '<div class=\"product_text\"><p> Direct equity investment can be very rewarding. Simultaneously this is also true that the risk of loss in direct equity is high. People who can balance risk and return while dealing with direct equity are the winners. But how can one balance the risk and reward? The risk associated with direct equity comes from the complexity of information. It\'s not so easy to decode information related to equity.</p><p> Direct equity investment can be very profitable if one is well versed with the critical know- hows and has a financial advisor, who with his expertise can make investors wealth grow by double digits.</p><p> With over 4000plus stocks listed on the exchange, Advisor Zaroori Hai aligns you with an exceptionally experienced advisor, who is dedicated to help you invest better. To connect with one, request a call back today!</p></div>'),
(8, 'debt', 'Debt', '<div class=\"product_text\"><p> The most distinguishing feature of the debt instruments of the Indian debt market is that the return is fixed. This means that the returns are almost risk-free.</p><p> India\'s debt market is one of the largest in Asia. Most often, the debt market in India is considered a useful substitute for banking channels for finance.</p><p> This fixed return on the bond is often termed as the \'coupon rate\' or the \'interest rate\'. Therefore, the buyer (of a bond) gives the seller a loan at a fixed interest rate, which equals the coupon rate.</p><p> Due to the availability of a plethora of debt instruments in the market with different ratings, selecting one or few becomes an arduous task. Hence creating a dire need for an advisor who can devote sufficient time to select the instrument to invest in on behalf of the investor.</p><p> Advisor Zaroori Hai connects you with an advisor who would ardently look in to providing the ideal instruments for you. Connect with us today!</p></div>'),
(9, 'unlisted-equity', 'Unlisted Equity', '<div class=\"product_text mb-5\"><p> Financial intermediaries often dupe unsuspecting and inexperienced investors by selling unlisted stocks. Unaware of the difference between listed and unlisted stocks, investors do not understand how each affects the value and liquidity of their investments.</p><p> There is nothing wrong with trading unlisted shares. However, there are some unhealthy practices that are prevalent in this business. Hence the need to choose an advisor to guide becomes supreme.</p><p> At Advisor Zaroori Hai, we understand the value of every penny earned and that is why we take the time to screen out the best stocks to help you make informed investments.</p></div><p>Some of the unlisted shares that are currently available in the market.</p><div class=\"product_text mb-5 text-left\"><table class=\"table realestate_table\"><thead><tr><th>Script Name</th><th>Sector</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>Syngenta</b></td><td>Mnc Agro chemical</td></tr><tr><td><b>HDB Financial</b></td><td>NBFC</td></tr><tr><td><b>Hdfc Securities</b></td><td>Broking financial</td></tr><tr><td><b>Utkarsh Mirco</b></td><td>Small Finance Bank</td></tr><tr><td><b>Suryoday Small Bank</b></td><td>Small Finance Bank</td></tr><tr><td><b>Paytm</b></td><td>Payment Bank</td></tr><tr><td><b>Finopayment Bank</b></td><td>Payment Bank</td></tr><tr><td><b>Sterlite Power</b></td><td>Power</td></tr><tr><td><b>Ncl Build tech</b></td><td>Building Material</td></tr><tr><td><b>Ncl Holding</b></td><td>parent</td></tr><tr><td><b>Hero Fincorp</b></td><td>NBFC</td></tr><tr><td><b>Capgemini</b></td><td>IT &amp; KPO</td></tr><tr><td><b>Uti Amc</b></td><td>Amc</td></tr><tr><td><b>Bira B9</b></td><td>Breweries</td></tr><tr><td><b>Mohan Mainking</b></td><td>Breweries</td></tr><tr><td><b>Cremica Agro</b></td><td>consumer product</td></tr><tr><td><b>Rivigo *</b></td><td>Logistic (Pvt equities)</td></tr><tr><td><b>Atlas Copco</b></td><td>Mnc</td></tr><tr><td><b>Essar St