(10, 'real-estate', 'Real Estate', '<div class=\"product_text mb-5\"><p> Cross-border real estate involves transacting or leasing property in another country. As there is a lot of money and land laws involved, a thorough due diligence is paramount to avoid possible risk of investing wrongly. It is imperative to understand the economic outlook of both the countries in terms of legal, tax, environmental, technical, and real estate and construction framework as each may vary vastly from the other country. That is why it is important to appoint a person /an entity who can advise the investor and carry out a thorough research on investor’s behalf to ensure a secure investment.</p><p> Having carried out scores of cross- border transactions, Advisor Zaroori Hai can help you own property overseas smoothly. To know more, connect with us today.</p></div><div class=\"product_text mb-5 text-left\"><table class=\"table realestate_table mb-5 border\"><thead><tr><th></th><th>LOCATION</th><th>PROJECT TYPE</th><th width=\"10%\">GUARANTEED RENTAL YIELD</th><th>TENURE</th><th class=\"text-right\">INVESTMENT AMOUNT</th><th class=\"text-right\">INVESTMENT AMOUNT (₹)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align: center; background-color: #e6f0ff\"><b>TOP YIELDING INVESTMENTS</b></td></tr><tr><td><b>Car Park Investment</b></td><td>Glasgow, UK</td><td>Commercial</td><td>11%</td><td>5-10 Years</td><td class=\"text-right\">£25,000</td><td class=\"text-right\">₹ 2,300,000</td></tr><tr><td><b> Student Accomodation Investment</b></td><td>Liverpool, UK</td><td>Commercial</td><td>9%</td><td>5 Years</td><td class=\"text-right\">£69,000</td><td class=\"text-right\">₹ 6,348,000</td></tr><tr><td><b>Student Accomodation Investment</b></td><td>Playmoth, UK</td><td>Commercial</td><td>8%</td><td>3 Years</td><td class=\"text-right\">£64,000</td><td class=\"text-right\">₹ 5,888,000</td></tr><tr><td><b>Hotel Investment</b></td><td>Liverpool, UK</td><td>Commercial</td><td>10%</td><td>10 Y